---

## Prerequisites

- **Python 3.6+** (tested on Python 3.8 & 3.10)
- Standard library modules only (`socket`, `argparse`, `logging`, `math`, etc.)
- No external dependencies; both scripts use only Python standard library.

---

## Setup

1. **Clone or unzip** this repository:

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/Harshvgupta/ipc_socket_communication.git
   cd imu_ipc_driver
   example commands to run it 
   Open two terminal and run these commands.

   1.python3 publisher.py   --socket-path /tmp/imu_socket   --log-level DEBUG   --frequency-hz 500

   2.python3 consumer.py   --socket-path /tmp/imu_socket   --timeout-ms 100   --log-dir ./logs   --log-level DEBUG

